				<div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> » <a href="/apps">Portable App Directory</a> » <a href="/apps/development">Development</a></div>						<h1>XAMPP</h1>
												<!-- start main content -->
				<div class="node">
    <div class="info"></div>
  <div class="content">
  <h2 class="tagline"><img width="150" height="44" align="right" alt="" src="/files/images/logos/xampp.png" />the complete, portable server</h2>
<p><a href="http://www.apachefriends.org/en/xampp.html">XAMPP</a> is an integrated server package of Apache, mySQL, PHP and Perl (the AMPP in XAMPP) that all run from a removable drive.  Everything is pre-configured and ready to go just by unzipping or installing it.</p>


<div class="download-box" style="float: left;"><a href="http://www.apachefriends.org/en/xampp-windows.html#641" class="download-link" title="Download XAMPP"><span><strong>Download XAMPP</strong> <em>1.7.3 for Windows<br />51MB download / 221MB installed</em></span></a> <a href="/apps/development/xampp#download_details">Download Details</a></div>

<div class="download-box" style="float: left;"><a href="http://www.apachefriends.org/en/xampp-windows.html#646" class="download-link" title="Download XAMPP Lite"><span><strong>Download XAMPP Lite</strong> <em>1.7.3 for Windows<br />28MB download / 116MB installed</em></span></a> <a href="/apps/development/xampp#download_details">Download Details</a></div>

<br class="clear" />

<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post">
	<input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_xclick" />
	<input type="hidden" name="business" value="xampp@apachefriends.org" />
	<input type="hidden" name="item_name" value="Apache Friends XAMPP" />
	<input type="hidden" name="no_shipping" value="1" />
